title: Don't miss out on this unique NY style industrial design studio loft
posting_body: ["%$&/Don't miss out on this unique NY style industrial design studio loft in the heart of Miami.", 'BRAND NEW KITCHEN ISLAND, Incredible open spaced unit with the option of having it furnished, high ceilings, washer and dryer and private balcony with a great view!', 'Building residents enjoy top amenities such as 24hr security, assigned parking, pool & jacuzzi and fitness center.', 'Centrally located and only minutes to Wynwood, Design District, Miami Beach, Downtown and MIA airport.%&$%', '#$%If you have been denied an application for lease in the past due to bad credit or your background, please call me or text me', 'show contact info', ', I will get you approved!!', 'Self-employed, bad credit, no problem.', 'Text me, I respond immediately and have tons of inventory!', 'WE ARE ESSENTIAL BUSINESS FOR COVI19, WE ARE ALWAYS OPEN', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'Andy Zamudio', 'show contact info', 'We accept deposits with credit card if you are short of cash we help with that, we are the only company that accepts credit cards for deposits , zelle, cash app, paypal venmo payments accepted!!!', 'Aceptamos los depositos con tarjeta de credito sinud esta corto de cash, somos la unica compañia que lo acepta en Florida, zelle, cash app, paypal ,venmo.']
